ite, old-fashioned boarding school in New England, a passionate English teacher inspires his students to rebel against convention and seize the potential of every day, courting the disdain of the stern headmaster.','55.458584','2.35860116E8','129.0','Released','He was their inspiration. He made their lives extraordinary.',8.1,2705);
